1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Ji.

2
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:09,200
Stop.

3
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:10,320
Liuchuan,

4
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,360
don't go too far.

5
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:12,120
As for what happened before,

6
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,760
I admit what I did was inappropriate.

7
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:15,320
But there's no need to keep badgering me.

8
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:16,440
I don't have time for you.

9
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,570
Where is your uncle?

10
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:20,360
My mother has already resolved this matter perfectly.

11
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:21,800
Why are you still looking for him?

12
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,000
Resolved perfectly?

13
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:24,120
So many people died.

14
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,980
You can't just say it's resolved.

15
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,320
The families of the casualties

16
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:29,120
have promised my mother not to pursue it.

17
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,520
Isn't it settled then?

18
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,440
You nobles

19
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:34,770
really don't take human lives seriously.

20
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,920
Your Highness,

21
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:40,420
what you call a resolution

22
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,320
is merely because they

23
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:43,120
were forced by the power of the Duke's Manor

24
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,320
to compromise.

25
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:46,000
But those are human lives.

26
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:48,320
If we don't find out the truth,

27
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,840
more people will die.

28
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:51,520
Let me be straight with you.

29
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,960
Given your uncle's current situation,

30
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:53,820
either he dies,

31
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,600
or a few more lives will be lost,

32
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:57,930
most likely people from the Duke's Manor.

33
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,240
You...

34
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:00,520
Don't scare me.

35
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:03,320
You saw it with your own eyes at the Chamber of Commerce.

36
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:05,180
Do you want the tragedy to repeat?

37
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,400
Pampered young ladies like her

38
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,800
need to be scared like this.

39
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,200
I'm not exaggerating.

40
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:15,380
I don't talk nonsense like you do.

41
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,000
Help!

42
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:33,320
Mother!

43
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,920
Step aside.

44
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,720
Don't touch him.

45
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,680
Brother!

46
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,040
Madam, please don't get close.

47
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,700
Be careful not to be infected.

48
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,400
It seems to find out the cause of death,

49
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,400
we have to perform an autopsy first.

50
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:09,970
How dare you!

51
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,640
Who allowed you to touch my brother's body?

52
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,640
Since you saved me today,

53
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,760
please leave.

54
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:20,770
What is this?

55
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:22,480
Don't break it.

56
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,079
Cheapskate.

57
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:26,000
If I break it, I'll pay for it.

58
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,440
You can't afford it.

59
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,120
Is there anything I can't afford?

60
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,200
You're bluffing.

61
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:32,920
Whatever I want,

62
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:33,920
I must have.

63
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:34,840
Including people,

64
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,680
it's the same.

65
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,280
How dare you.

66
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:40,770
How dare you!

67
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,079
You dare push me, the princess?

68
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:44,010
Careful, or you'll lose your head.

69
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,540
You and your mother are exactly the same.

70
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:47,120
Fine.

71
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,079
I won't pretend anymore.

72
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:49,880
I'm laying my cards on the table.

73
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,280
The imperially bestowed Liuye Sword is here.

74
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,040
Seeing it is like seeing His Majesty.

75
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:55,040
Duchess, Princess, heed the order.

76
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:58,579
What are you...

77
00:03:59,079 --> 00:03:59,600
Shut up!

78
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,720
This is indeed an item bestowed by His Majesty.

79
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,040
Mother, are you joking?

80
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:05,760
He...

81
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,720
His Majesty bestowed the Liuye blade upon me.

82
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,650
With this blade,

83
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,640
I can dissect all corpses in the world,

84
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,079
and solve unsolved cases

85
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,519
with no taboos.

86
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,320
Respect this.

87
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,519
Madam Guogong.

88
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,480
At this point,

89
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,000
you wouldn't want your brother

90
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,720
to die an unexplained death, would you?

91
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,120
Why not let Liu Chuan try?

92
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,440
Maybe he can find the cause of death

93
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,570
and the real killer.

94
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,200
That's all we can do.

95
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:53,610
The deceased must have inhaled

96
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:56,000
a large amount of powder particles before death.

97
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,920
Similar to

98
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:58,200
fern spores.

99
00:04:59,159 --> 00:04:59,760
Tweezers.

100
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,000
Hammer.

101
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:15,370
It seems that after the spores enter the body,

102
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:17,380
they grow into this kind of thing,

103
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,480
multiplying and spreading,

104
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,940
and releasing toxins.

105
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:24,240
This thing is very likely the culprit causing the disease

106
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:26,320
and driving the deceased mad.

107
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,040
And we cannot rule out the risk

108
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,840
of secondary fungal infection.

109
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:33,920
The Chamber of Commerce wants to tear down the temple,

110
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,120
and the Princess's uncle

111
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:37,040
happens to be the president of the Chamber.

112
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,040
It seems someone

113
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,440
wants to start with him

114
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,040
to deter those

115
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,640
who want to tear down the temple.

116
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:44,640
The effect will surely be excellent.

117
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,640
But this move is too vicious.

118
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,240
You scared me to death!

119
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:59,520
Your best friend is too scary.

120
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,440
She sold all her family property

121
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,440
just to find a place to stay with you.

122
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,240
I'm still worried about you.

123
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,080
Didn't you like her before?

124
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,840
I thought the dignified Miss Tu

125
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:14,680
would have a lot of resources to help me attract investment.

126
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,400
Who knew she was so reclusive

127
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:18,130
and scared away so many people?

128
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,720
Watch your mouth.

129
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:22,840
Master,

130
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:24,080
you've been away for the last two nights.

131
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:26,240
Miss Tu keeps telling me ghost stories,

132
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,040
so I'm too scared to sleep.

133
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:32,040
I heard the Plague Boy has returned recently.

134
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,080
How is it going?

135
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:37,640
You are interested in this too?

136
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,900
This is the Plague Boy.

137
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,840
Ever since the last time at the God of Medicine Temple,

138
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,640
I have been looking for it.

139
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,640
There are even recorders

140
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:50,500
who saw it with their own eyes.

141
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,600
Yes, Master.

142
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:53,640
Miss Tu spent a lot of money on this.

143
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,080
It breaks my heart to see.

144
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,280
People used to say

145
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,920
you were a spendthrift, Master.

146
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,080
I think Miss Tu

147
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,200
is no different.

148
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,600
I can't talk her out of it.

149
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,460
How will this end if it continues?

150
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:11,280
Can you tell me all

151
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,440
the information you have

152
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,600
about Wentongzi?

153
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:16,640
I'm afraid one night is not enough to tell you everything.

154
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,240
It's fine.

155
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:19,140
I will stay with you all night.

156
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,160
That would be great.

157
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,480
It's nothing.

158
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:33,240
I'll return to the county office to verify some clues.

159
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,840
Be careful, Yunmeng.

160
00:08:57,800 --> 00:09:00,000
You don't really need a blanket to read.

161
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:12,520
Time has passed so quickly.

162
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,120
This must be

163
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,640
what Einstein called the theory of relativity.

164
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:18,840
Sitting across from a beautiful woman

165
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,520
makes time fly.

166
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:23,080
But sitting on a hot stove

167
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,810
makes it feel like an eternity.

168
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,440
Then this Mr. Ai

169
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,940
makes quite a lot of sense.

170
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:36,320
Ten years ago,

171
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,760
Qu San's son

172
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,840
was chosen as the Plague Child.

173
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,000
As expected, the victim is related to the temple renovation again.

174
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:11,800
Look.

175
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:22,300
It's the same as the last clue.

176
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:26,300
It seems it's no coincidence.

177
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:01,640
Mother.
